 <title>Supported Software</title>
 <para>
  <emphasis role="bold">Supported ESXi versions</emphasis>
 </para>
 <para>
  &kw-hos-phrase; currently supports the following ESXi versions:
 </para>
 <itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    ESXi version 6.0
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    ESXi version 6.0 (Update 1b)
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    ESXi version 6.5
   </para>
  </listitem>
 </itemizedlist>
 <para>
  The following are the requirements for your vCenter server:
 </para>
 <itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Software: vCenter (It is recommended to run the same server version as the
    ESXi hosts.)
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    License Requirements: vSphere Enterprise Plus license
   </para>
  </listitem>
 </itemizedlist>
</section>
